{"id":238868,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/07/法国人拍洋民工在中国/","date":"2012-07-09T22:01:05Z","modified":"2012-07-09T22:01:05Z","title":"法国人拍洋民工在中国","content":"<p>在武汉待了六年的法国人Benoit Cezard不经意间在中国的网络上红了一把，起因是他导演拍摄了一组“洋民工在中国”，假设2050年前后中国一枝独秀，那些原本由农民工承担的角色如小贩、清洁工、“麻木”司机便换上了洋面孔。（文字来源：南方都市报）</p>\n<p>Benoit Cezard的关于该项目的网站，总组共有9张图片。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.benoitcezard.com/projects/china-2050/\">http://www.benoitcezard.com/projects/china-2050/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://discovery.163.com/photoview/4T8F0001/25262.html#p=85Q8DUPP4T8F0001\">http://discovery.163.com/photoview/4T8F0001/25262.html#p=85Q8DUPP4T8F0001</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.51labour.com/show/173633.html\">http://www.51labour.com/show/173633.html</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Benoit Cezard：China 2050</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/28_china-006.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-238870\" title=\"é¥æ§å 006\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/28_china-006.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"509\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/28_china-006.jpg 800w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/28_china-006-300x238.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/28_benoit-cezardchina-205007.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-238869\" title=\"28_benoit-cezardchina-205007\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/28_benoit-cezardchina-205007.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"508\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/28_benoit-cezardchina-205007.jpg 800w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/28_benoit-cezardchina-205007-300x238.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://chinadigita